 Archives for UIMA's Eclipse Update Site

The Apache UIMA™ project keeps older versions of Eclipse Update Sites in the Apache archive. These are organized by subsites:

  • uimaj - for the core UIMA Java project
  • others - to be added when the archive is created.

The naming convention is to start with the subsite's main name such as uimaj or ruta, and then suffix this with "-a.b.c-d.e.f" where a.b.c represents the earliest version and d.e.f is the last version included.

uimaj-2.3.1-2.10.1
